Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭和之后做的那些理也理不清的杂事结束之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快地  能够听见在冬天的脚步声伴随着山风一起到来的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是快到12月了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.28,0:00:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夸耀着和学校同龄的古老的这座社团教室大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于墙壁太过单薄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在室内  也会感觉有些寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:08.07,staffbiaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\a3}Someday in the Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都会被卷入各种各样事件的SOS团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来其实主要都是集中在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这种事也不是每天都会一定会遇上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:03:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果每天都有这样那样的超常事件炸弹爆炸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体也会支撑不住  心灵更是早就该崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（圣诞节恋爱占卜  去寻找幸福吧！圣诞特辑）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  春日不在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是安静得令人高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…是不是太安静了点？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想  遇到春日和朝比奈学姐以来已经半年了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是经历了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很多的起因都是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有些并非如此的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢  基本上都是在我们悠闲地品味生活时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙突然冲进来而开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！听我说  有好消息哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙嘴里说的好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:04:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我们  特别是我和朝比奈学姐来说  真的是好消息的例子几乎没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在社团教室里面装暖气设备了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍电影的时候做过赞助商的那个电器店  说会为我们提供设备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是有去年卖剩下的电暖气  囤积在仓库里一直忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理掉觉得可惜  如果我们愿意就可以拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才打电话来说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界上应该没有会闲到特地打电话\N给春日说这种事的亲切电器商
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以估计又是这家伙去强要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此呢  阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在去店里把它拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去？现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  你现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  是打算让我把每天都来回往返的那段坡道再下去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还要去再坐2站电车才能到的电器店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要再搬着东西回来这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  因为如果你不快去的话  说不定那个大叔就改主意了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  快点给我去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得进了这间屋子的人没有一个不闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道就不闲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之后还有必须要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉是副团长  而你只是平头团员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论哪个组织都是等级较低的人要做更重的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然SOS团也采用了这种规则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  这次总算还是个能理解的正经任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我知道了  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}请小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊  我也和你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好也想在社团教室里装个暖气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其推给朝比奈学姐或者长门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如我自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}这种杂活可以说就是他的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点！快去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  碍事的人也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}  我要拍几张照片  来摆些POSE吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦～？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请  请问是什么照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗？当然是因为文化祭的时候上映的\N「朝比奈实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}的冒险」要做成DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要拍照片作封面啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…真的要做出来吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是放弃了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个时候阿虚太罗嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就不会有人反对了吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始爬这条坡路上学的时候可是厌烦得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是经过了半年之后  也已经完全适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是像徒步旅行路线的上下学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是SOS团…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  春日又趁我不在的时候在社团教室做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不是说着因为无聊或者别的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就肆意玩弄朝比奈学姐就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉  拿反光板的任务就交给你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}  别发呆了  快摆POSE啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得再有诱惑力一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表现出「想要」的样子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度勾引不到男人啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该换身衣服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己会换的——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦！我帮你换比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？连胸罩也要一起…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也要脱下来  没关系吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}  你的是不是又变大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越爆了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…你你你你在摸哪里啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经凉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好害羞哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}  你应该更有自信一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  你可是我亲自挑出来的学校里第一的吉祥物角色啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是说得太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来穿这个吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所  所以那个  我自己来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要在今天之内拍完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要抓紧时间！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是这件护士服还是那一件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有在电影里出现…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是为了DVD封面拍摄的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在我突然有了一个主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍了这么多都可以编成写真集了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个主意你觉得怎么样？古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这真是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要做DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该拍些附赠影像出来呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉  你觉得这个主意怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个异常好的主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车即将进站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  把背面转向我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来恐怕要下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:06.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  把这个戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快脱下来快脱下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦～还要继续吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想脱吗～？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用脱这个也可以了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要放在店头的  所以当然不能有这个啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的相会～这轮回的记忆～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是约好要给你们的电暖气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拿得回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些可爱的女孩子们还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中有一个因为太有精神了  弄得我很麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广告的效果表现出来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  和以前没什么变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来也是啊  高中文化祭上的电影中间插入的广告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局限性也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还真能拉到赞助商啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  那个很精神的女孩子在电话里对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要拍电影的续篇  是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那家伙这么说了  估计就真的会拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拜托我继续赞助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个电暖气就当作是下次赞助的前金吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是耍了这种伎俩啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水黾水黾  好红好红  {\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}a i u e o{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在浮藻里  小虾也在  游啊游着泳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柿子的树  栗子的树  {\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}ka ki ku ke ko{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啄木鸟  在咯咯地  啄着枯榉树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在豇豆上  浇上点醋  {\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}sa shi su se so{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条小鱼  在浅滩处  被人刺中了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来吧  喇叭出来  {\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}ta chi tsu te to{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}to to{\r}！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪唧啪唧  啪啪啪地  飞起来啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个蛞蝓  蠕动蠕动  {\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}na ni nu ne no{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～你就是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  红方选择了14号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～没关系  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来究竟会有怎样的发展呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请开始下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…那孩子刚一出来  舞台上的气氛就变了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个孩子…和之前完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起刚才  简直像是换了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个可怕的孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤面定食！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒饭定食！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸虾大碗盖饭定食！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年A（{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ace{\r}）！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中年A（{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ace{\r}）！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定年A（{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ace{\r}）！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（定年是退休年龄的意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留年A（{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ace{\r}）！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（留年即留级）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来年A（{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ace{\r}）！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（来年即明年）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残年A（{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ace{\r}）！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（残年是余生的意思，这里也可以当作是“残念”（遗憾的意思））
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是喜欢啊…A（{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ace{\r}）！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能做到最好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我努力！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想说的话已经被我完全彻底一点不剩地看透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像个小孩  内部却很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇子上强有力的伙伴  他的名字就是  名侦探——！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿～让开让开让开！你们没有看到这个家徽吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我是法国的  女王～～～～～呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被打中奇怪的地方啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还太嫩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好～我们是{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ice Candies{\r}！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Yuki{\r}～你还是那么性感啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看哪里啊你这色鬼  我可要叫警察了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就给了我一记下钩拳？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就好像是在环状线电车上被误当作色狼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来已经到冬天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对～是冬天了～一说起冬天——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是罗嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来一拳  真是厉害啊  小{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Yuki{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WBC也会邀请你加入吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待会不会有候补人选和我搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的期待可真阴沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…你看  这不是很快就要到圣诞节了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点想吃火锅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对！说到冬天就是火锅了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢在火锅里放些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这个嘛  比如白菜啊  猪肉  菌类…纳豆…豆腐…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Yuki{\r}呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇——！小{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Yuki{\r}是猎人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是赶快逃跑吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一想到熊的感受  就会觉得它太可怜了  吃不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你最初就不要把熊肉放进锅里去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来扮演那个在滚汤里煮的熊肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？小{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Yuki{\r}来演？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你扮演锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:14:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要最…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不出来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搬东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  还真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是凉宫的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来经过了半年  同学们对我的处境已经十分了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还要回学校去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  真下起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气预报明明说降水概率10%的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个胡说八道的气象预报员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望别下得太大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？下起雨来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的我没有比现在更留恋那间房子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想尽快喝到朝比奈学姐泡的热茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖我的身体和心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…咦？只有小长门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和她交换明天的值日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才来找她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  在那边吗  谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  阿虚出去办事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤屋学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦～辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  都淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕一会儿和这个一起交给实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一样  还是一个无法掌握行动的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但依旧是个亲切的好学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？…长门  只有你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日她们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！这里就应该坐上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很明白嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个笨拙女孩的样子实在是太惹人喜爱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是故意装出来的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉  帮我拿一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该这样  这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有些介意他们三个现在到底去哪里做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是抱着那么重的东西爬坡实在是把我打垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这条路在放学回家的时候还必须再走一遍  真是郁闷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧来吧来吧来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～手好冷啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一个人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会对我的脸做了什么恶作剧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会做这种幼稚的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他三个人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经先回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你总是睡不醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就留下来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在睡  又必须有人把社团教室的门锁上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还下着雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛线外套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件是春日的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  另一件是谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…等一下  这也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐在睡着的我身边换了衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！为什么睡得这么死！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是装作睡着的话…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  早就到了该回家的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真糟糕啊  我没带雨伞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一把就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往这边靠一点啦  我都淋到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经靠过去很多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这把伞不是你的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着「教职员工用」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是学校的预备品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让学生用一下也没什么不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？如果你想淋着雨回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不给你打了～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都把电暖气搬来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连句慰劳的话都不说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个团长大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.07,0:22:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦！
